                            </a>
                        </span> -->
                        <a href="https://airpax.co/" style="color: #2a9d8f; text-decoration: none;">airpax.co</a>
                    </p>

                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">We hope to serve you again in the future!</p>

                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">Best regards,<br>
                    <strong>Airpax Team</strong></p>

                    <div class="footer" style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 12px;"><strong>RIGI TRANS TECH PVT LTD</strong></p>
